txt.en: You sense a terrible presence nearby, old, evil, with all its ill-will bent upon you....
You have helped to defeat Venomtongue
Upon wandering into the den of salamanders in the northern Wold, a great fear has come over you. Something terrible lurks here.
Upon wandering into the den of salamanders in the northern Wold, a great fear has come over you. Something terrible lurks here.
A cruel old salamander by the name of Venomtongue has roamed these ruins for far too long.\n\nYou should defeat Venomtongue, for he has been allowed to endure for too many long years.
You have defeated one of the most vicious salamanders in the Wold, old Venomtongue of the Seething Mire.
